WEBVTT

00:00:00.574 --> 00:00:02.361
Africa is booming.

00:00:02.361 --> 00:00:04.866
Per capita incomes since the year 2000

00:00:04.866 --> 00:00:06.466
have doubled,

00:00:06.466 --> 00:00:09.841
and this boom is impacting on everyone.

00:00:09.841 --> 00:00:12.667
Life expectancy has increased by one year

00:00:12.667 --> 00:00:15.417
every three years for the last decade.

00:00:15.417 --> 00:00:18.902
That means if an African child is born today,

00:00:18.902 --> 00:00:20.690
rather than three days ago,

00:00:20.690 --> 00:00:22.577
they will get an extra day of life

00:00:22.577 --> 00:00:24.600
at the end of their lifespan.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.391
It's that quick.

00:00:26.391 --> 00:00:30.503
